      <item>
        <title>So given the 2.1.0 changes</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[NuclearBurrito]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>We need more sources of temporary occupy immunity and scum healing.</p>
<p>Ideas:</p>
<p>Herbalist drug actually heals their target and can target Unseen including themselves. It gets an additional use.</p>
<p>Enforcer protects grants temporary occupy immunity to the target in addition to its other effects</p>
<p>Ritualist brotherhood heals the target and gives them occupy immunity in addition to its current effects</p>
<p>For BD the CW always gives occupy immunity to the target regardless of type. The type specific effect on support is changed to making their effects impossible to bypass (Empowered Physician can heal Reap)</p>
          <p><a href="https://fol-archive.netlify.app/t/so-given-the-2-1-0-changes/74057/1">Read full topic</a></p>
